(twig snaps)

01:24:27.397 --> 01:24:29.607
(dog barking in distance)

01:24:38.116 --> 01:24:40.326
♪♪ (radio: jazz)

01:24:46.040 --> 01:24:49.669
♪♪ (jazz continues)

01:25:04.809 --> 01:25:07.103
- ♪♪ (continues)
